name: Tennyson's End
description:
This is a work of fiction.

They wouldn't let me publish the truth.

It all started at the auction.

An old manuscript turns up, and you've been asked to investigate. 

It would have been better for everyone if you hadn't.

Tennyson's End is a short, interactive story about aliens, the fey, and old, forgotten manuscripts. It's been described as "Literary sci fi horror", which seems as appropriate a genre as any.
